node.accessibility_caption: Photo by MELANIE ANABALON 🌱♌️🇦🇷 in Dallas, Texas with @theomegafitness. May be an image of 1 person, long hair, standing, activewear and indoor.

node.text: I didn’t eat the most nutritious diet while I was away on vacation so my belly has been hurting a tad bit. What I’m gonna do is take gut pills (from @xmajesticas ) focus on eating less processed foods, consume leafy greens, eat vegetables, exercise & lots of water 💦☺️ Oh & these leggings are from @theomegafitness I absolutely love them 😍
